title: Converse CONS  - Graffiti Artist Kaput
description:
Graffiti artist Kaput takes us on a nostalgic trip through the concrete jungle of NYC, as we watch what he does best and reminisce about the city of lights that continues to be a source of inspiration.


Credits:
Filmed & directed by: Will Robson Scott
Edited by: Luca Campanale

Music by: Lou Champagne System, “Silent Walking” (Medical Records)
